And so it's gonna be an amazing, an amazing nine week series, and then I'll lead this into at the movies, and then you'll after that is Christmas.

16:30.975 --> 16:31.595
That's crazy.

16:32.517 --> 16:34.580
All right, I know Pastor Blake is super excited about that.

16:34.640 --> 16:38.706
